quote.p:
Begin text: “Whereas Austria, in the
                                proclamation of April 27, 1945, solemnly declared the restoration of
                                her independence;

“Whereas Austria is convinced that, as an independent, sovereign and
                                free state, she can make her special contribution toward the
                                maintenance of world peace and order in Europe;

“The Federal Government is requested to submit to the Nationalrat
                                (Parliament) the draft of a Federal constitutional law regulating
                                the neutrality;

“To take all steps in order to achieve the final admission to the
                                organization of the United Nations, for which Austria has already
                                applied on — 1947;
